cations to astellas for the european south africa and middle east territories in february  prior to joining fibrogen in  he was at the drug delivery company aradigm where he was a director of business development and marketing from  to  since  mr hodder has held sales marketing and product development positions at penederm now bertek pharmaceuticals ciba geigy now novartis bristol‐myers squibb company and marion laboratories now sanofi aventis mr hodder completed his undergraduate studies at oakland university with a bs in biology and holds an mba from the university of chicago booth school of business and has been invited to speak at numerous licensing eventsexperiencesenior vice president corporate developmentprotagonist therapeuticsdecember  – present  years  monthssan francisco bay areacorporatebusiness development consultantbiopharma strategy and consulting – december   yearssan francisco bay areaassist private prefunded and funded and public biotech companies with various fundraising corporate development licensing and marketing activitiesvice president business developmentpromedior incdecember  – july   monthsgreater boston areacofounderceotrenovus inc – december   yearssan francisco bay areafounded company to seek funding for the development of ldn a small molecule bmpalk receptor kinase inhibitor discovered at massachusetts generalbrigham and women’s hospital and the discovery of nd generation alk inhibitorsvice president business developmentfibrogen incapril  – january   years  monthssan francisco bay areacorporate officer and member of the executive management team responsible for all licensing and ma activity and ongoing partner alliance management managed a team of  –  professionalssignificant activities included• outlicensing of hif prolyl hydroxylase inhibitors for anemia indications to yamanouchi for the japan territory in april  deal terms included m cash upfront m equity investment and significant development and sales milestones• outlicensing of h